Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:07.71,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Like a cruel angel{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:14.59,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Become a legend, young boy{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:30.40,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}When a blue wind{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Knocks on the door to your heart{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:37.57,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You just gaze back at me{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}And smile oh so gently{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:45.25,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}So eager for something{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You touch so softly{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:52.59,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Those innocent eyes{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:59.30,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But one day, you will realize{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}That upon your back{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:07.06,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You have wings{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You can fly to the faraway future{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:11.57,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The cruel angel's thesis{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:15.45,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}One day, you'll take off through a window{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:19.20,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}If your overflowing pathos{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:22.70,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Leads you to betray your memories{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:26.62,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:30.59,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Become legend, young boy{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:37.13,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Hello. I'm not home right now.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Leave a message after the beep.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:43.10,default,,0,0,0,,One last job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:46.35,default,,0,0,0,,It's the same color as blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.98,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\Nthe deputy commander's been abducted?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:53.69,default,,0,0,0,,It happened two hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:57.32,default,,0,0,0,,His last confirmed location\Nwas in Ward Eight in the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.16,default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's inside this facility!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.41,default,,0,0,0,,Were you guys at Intel asleep on the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:04.62,default,,0,0,0,,They had an inside man who was\Nleaking Intel and stirring up trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.79,default,,0,0,0,,He gave us the runaround.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:09.54,default,,0,0,0,,A man who could outwit Intel Section Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:10.67,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.63,default,,0,0,0,,Ryoji Kaji. We believe him to be\Nthe mastermind behind the disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:17.38,default,,0,0,0,,Which is why you came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.43,default,,0,0,0,,It's helpful that you catch on so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:24.43,default,,0,0,0,,As colleagues, we hate having to suspect\Nour own chief of operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.22,default,,0,0,0,,but this is our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:30.52,default,,0,0,0,,Considering my history with him,\Nit's the logical step to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.48,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation. Bring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.40,default,,0,0,0,,It's been quite some time, Chairman Keel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.74,default,,0,0,0,,This is a rather rough welcome,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:42.49,default,,0,0,0,,Apologies for rude behavior\Nare not warranted here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:46.83,default,,0,0,0,,We needed to have an uninterrupted chat.\NIt was the logical step to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:51.04,default,,0,0,0,,You never change. My convenience\Nhas never been a concern for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:55.50,default,,0,0,0,,This matter requires immediate attention.\NIt couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.38,default,,0,0,0,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:00.93,default,,0,0,0,,It must be, if you're appearing to me\Nas Seele rather than the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:04.18,default,,0,0,0,,We have no intention\Nof creating a new god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.22,default,,0,0,0,,We require your assistance,\NProfessor Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.60,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}"Professor Fuyutsuki," is it?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.69,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Professor! Professor Fuyutsuki!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.40,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.07,default,,0,0,0,,Have any plans, sir?\NWant to grab a beer at Kamogawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.28,default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:24.62,default,,0,0,0,,Ryoko and her friends say they'll come,\Nbut only if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.54,default,,0,0,0,,The other professors say you ought\Nto join in every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.33,default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.83,default,,0,0,0,,It's good for you to go out\Nfor a drink every now and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:34.96,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:38.13,default,,0,0,0,,You're very talented,\Nbut you should give more thought
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.92,default,,0,0,0,,to cultivating relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.13,default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that to heart, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:45.55,default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Fuyutsuki,\Nthere's a student over in Bioengineering
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:47.89,default,,0,0,0,,who's put together a fascinating report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.60,default,,0,0,0,,Do you know a student\Nby the name of Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.98,default,,0,0,0,,Ikari? No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.94,default,,0,0,0,,When I mentioned you and your work, Ikari\Nexpressed an interest in meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.24,default,,0,0,0,,This student will be in touch soon.\NBe accommodating, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.20,default,,0,0,0,,"Ikari," was it? Very well, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.74,default,,0,0,0,,METAPHYSICAL BIO, LAB NO.1\N(FUYUTSUKI)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.12,default,,0,0,0,,I've taken the liberty\Nof reading your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.37,default,,0,0,0,,There are a few points I'm not sold on,\Nbut it was a stimulating read.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.21,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.46,default,,0,0,0,,"Yui Ikari," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:15.75,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.75,default,,0,0,0,,What are your plans after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:21.63,default,,0,0,0,,Get a job in the private sector?\NOr take a position at a lab here, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:27.01,default,,0,0,0,,I haven't thought that far ahead yet.\NAnd isn't there also a third option?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:33.02,default,,0,0,0,,I've also thought about starting a family.\NAssuming I meet the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.19,default,,0,0,0,,AGAIN, IN 2015 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.81,default,,0,0,0,,By assimilating that S2 Drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.19,default,,0,0,0,,it has attained absolute existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.15,default,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.82,default,,0,0,0,,A manifested god is of no use to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.20,default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't create a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:51.95,default,,0,0,0,,Much less allow it\Nto fall into that man's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:55.46,default,,0,0,0,,Gendoh Ikari... Can this man be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.92,default,,0,0,0,,Gendoh Rokubungi?\NYes, I've heard the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.75,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}No, I've never personally met him.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:05.05,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But he is the sort of man{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}whose reputation precedes him.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.47,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}What? He's asking to be released{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}into {\c}{\i0}my{\i1\c&Hffffff&} custody?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.81,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}No, I'll come down.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}When would be a good time?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.81,default,,0,0,0,,I heard about you from a mutual friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.44,default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet you for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:23.53,default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting you to be\Nthe trashy sort who gets into bar brawls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.90,default,,0,0,0,,He took a swing at me\Nbefore I could talk my way out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:30.91,default,,0,0,0,,Being liked makes me uncomfortable.\NI'm far more used to being an outcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:35.12,default,,0,0,0,,Well, your social skills\Nhave nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:40.25,default,,0,0,0,,Prof. Fuyutsuki, you seem to be exactly\Nthe sort of man I hoped you would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:45.26,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}My first impression was that he{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}was a thoroughly unpleasant man.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:50.22,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}It was autumn at the time. This was back{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}when this country still had seasons.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.68,default,,0,0,0,,-Is that true?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.31,default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a relationship with Mr. Rokubungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:59.31,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I could not hide my surprise{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}when I heard those words.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.27,default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you have anything in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:08.15,default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Professor Fuyutsuki.\NHe's actually very charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.86,default,,0,0,0,,No one knows it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.70,default,,0,0,0,,Then perhaps ignorance really is bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.95,default,,0,0,0,,Was my introducing you an imposition?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:21.33,default,,0,0,0,,No. He's an interesting man, to be sure.\NBut I can't bring myself to like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:27.22,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}In my circles, it was widely thought that{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}he had fostered a relationship with Yui{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.09,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}to gain access to her talents{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}and the group she was associated with.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:35.26,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Later on, I heard rumors that{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}this group's name was "Seele."{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.77,default,,0,0,0,,ANTARCTICA, 2000 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.77,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The Second Impact.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.94,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}That tragedy struck{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}in the final year of the 20th Century.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:46.53,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}And the first year of the 21st Century{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}could only be described as Hell.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.03,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}There are no other words{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}to describe that year.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.36,default,,0,0,0,,2002 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.79,default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe that this\Nwas once a continent of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.70,default,,0,0,0,,It's utterly unrecognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:06:59.41,default,,0,0,0,,Professor Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.92,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.\NI'm amazed you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:07.34,default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were on\Nthe Katsuragi Expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:10.51,default,,0,0,0,,As luck would have it, I had returned\Nto Japan the day beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.14,default,,0,0,0,,so I managed to avoid the tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.47,default,,0,0,0,,I see. Look, Rokubungi--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.85,default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Professor,\Nbut I've changed my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.15,default,,0,0,0,,A postcard? Not a business card?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.56,default,,0,0,0,,WE'RE MARRIED!\NGENDOH AND YUI IKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.69,default,,0,0,0,,Ikari... Gendoh {\i1\c&Hffffff&}Ikari?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:31.82,default,,0,0,0,,The missus insisted that I give this\Nto you, Professor. She's quite the fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.70,default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.95,default,,0,0,0,,So, how is Yui? She's not coming\Non this field expedition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:42.08,default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to come with us,\Nbut we have a child now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.88,default,,0,0,0,,This organization you belong to.\NSeele, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.80,default,,0,0,0,,I've heard nothing but bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:52.13,default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I approve of the way\Nthey strong-arm the Security Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.59,default,,0,0,0,,As principled as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:57.60,default,,0,0,0,,But these days, no organization\Nthat plays by the rules can survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:01.48,default,,0,0,0,,This official investigation\Nof the Second Impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:05.94,default,,0,0,0,,It would raise suspicions if it were\Ncomposed entirely of Seele members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.15,default,,0,0,0,,That's why the rest of us\Nwere brought in, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.45,default,,0,0,0,,2015 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.74,default,,0,0,0,,NERV ISOLATION FACILITY NO.4
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:19.41,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I still don't like dark places.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Bad things always come back to me.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.00,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Who is she?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.96,default,,0,0,0,,The sole survivor\Nof the original expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:24.96,default,,0,0,0,,2002 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.92,default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Misato Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:29.84,default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi? The daughter\Nof {\i1\c&Hffffff&}Doctor {\c}{\i0}Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:33.42,default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She hasn't spoken a single word\Nin nearly two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.09,default,,0,0,0,,That poor girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.09,default,,0,0,0,,Whatever she saw,\Nit was bad enough to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:41.47,default,,0,0,0,,Mental trauma can take longer to heal\Nthan simple physical injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.43,default,,0,0,0,,Very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.65,default,,0,0,0,,Releasing our findings\Nwill require careful attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:49.98,default,,0,0,0,,Everything about this\Ngiant of light is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:54.95,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Afterwards, the UN would officially report{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}that the Second Impact was caused by{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.82,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}the impact of a meteor of enormous mass.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:02.70,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}In my eyes, however,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}it was clear that this was a cover-up.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:08.08,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I could catch hints of Seele, and a man{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}called Keel, at work behind the scenes.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:12.05,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I wanted to learn more about{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}the dark truth behind this incident.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:16.09,default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1\c&Hffffff&}Even if the name "Yui Ikari" popped up.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.39,default,,0,0,0,,Why would you conceal\Nthe existence of the giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.93,default,,0,0,0,,Your group knew the Second Impact\Nwas coming, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.89,default,,0,0,0,,You knew it would happen that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:32.11,default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned that you were lucky enough\Nto leave the day before the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:36.70,default,,0,0,0,,Was it also luck that you gathered all of\Nyour research material before you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:42.33,default,,0,0,0,,I thought all those\Nhad been incinerated. I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:45.41,default,,0,0,0,,I've looked into your finances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.54,default,,0,0,0,,I realize that it takes\Na lot of money to raise a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.09,default,,0,0,0,,but don't you think you have far more\Nthan any individual needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.63,default,,0,0,0,,Impressive as ever, Professor Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:55.80,default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should change\Nyour field to economics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.51,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going public with how your Seele group
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:01.76,default,,0,0,0,,and the Dead Sea Scrolls\Nare connected to the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.52,default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to let those responsible\Nget away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.18,default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:09.35,default,,0,0,0,,But before you do that,\Nthere's something I want you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.73,default,,0,0,0,,We're certainly going down a long way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.94,default,,0,0,0,,-Does that worry you?\N-Somewhat, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:19.41,default,,0,0,0,,What on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.95,default,,0,0,0,,A structure that was left behind\Nby someone who wasn't us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:25.33,default,,0,0,0,,Eighty-nine percent of it is buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.91,default,,0,0,0,,Then this was originally a perfectly\Nspherical underground space?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:33.67,default,,0,0,0,,All of mankind's resources\Nare being poured into that installation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.14,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Professor Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.64,default,,0,0,0,,Akagi? You're involved in this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:45.89,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.10,default,,0,0,0,,This is the best place to work out\Nthe basic theories
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.64,default,,0,0,0,,underpinning the biological computers\NI'm trying to create.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:54.52,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to call them the Magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:57.61,default,,0,0,0,,Magi? The three wise men from the East?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.61,default,,0,0,0,,-Is that what you wanted to show me?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:02.57,default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.49,default,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko, we'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:11.00,default,,0,0,0,,What on earth...\NSurely you didn't bring that giant here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:14.21,default,,0,0,0,,We Gehirn members\Nrefer to that object as "Adam."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.80,default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the giant.\NIt's not the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.76,default,,0,0,0,,-So this is...\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.68,default,,0,0,0,,This is Eva, created by man from Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.30,default,,0,0,0,,Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:30.23,default,,0,0,0,,This is the prototype of the Adam\NRebirth Project, also called Project-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.39,default,,0,0,0,,Eva-00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.11,default,,0,0,0,,The prototype of a {\i1\c&Hffffff&}god?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:39.19,default,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki, will you join me in forging\Na new history for mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.03,default,,0,0,0,,2015 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.70,default,,0,0,0,,Um, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:52.25,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.\NLet's get Rei re-tested right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.83,default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Ms. Katsuragi around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.54,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I hadn't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.46,default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:01.17,default,,0,0,0,,Yep, Misato Katsuragi!\NPleased to meet'cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:06.30,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Mother, I met a girl named{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Katsuragi the other day.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.47,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}People tend to give me a wide berth.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.77,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Whenever that happens, it drives home{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}how much weight your name carries.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:16.56,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But not her. She's totally at ease{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}around me for some reason.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:21.11,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I learned that she was the sole survivor{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}of that doomed expedition.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.86,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}She says she lost the ability{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}to speak for a while,{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:27.74,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}but the way she goes on and on now,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}it's like she's making up for lost time.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:32.79,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Ritchan, I'm still spending{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}all my time underground here.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.25,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'm really tired of the boxed{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}lunches they give us.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.75,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The Tokyo-3 project is underway topside{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:40.96,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}as part of the 2nd Capital{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Transfer Project.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.76,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Misato was away from school for a while,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}and when I made her tell me why,{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.09,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I couldn't believe it.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.97,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}She said she'd been in bed{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}with her boyfriend the whole time.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:53.31,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}They had just stayed there in bed{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}for a whole week.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:56.48,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I feel like I've learned about a side{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}to her I never knew existed.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.69,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}She introduced me to him today.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:02.78,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}He's handsome, but I'll never get used{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}to that carefree attitude of his.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.49,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Boys have never been your strong suit,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}have they, Ritchan?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.58,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Maybe being raised by a single mother...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:13.70,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'm sorry. I was never{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}a hands-on parent, was I?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:16.67,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'm terrible, I only act like a mother{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}when it doesn't take any effort.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.34,default,,0,0,0,,Act like a mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.42,default,,0,0,0,,2004 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.84,default,,0,0,0,,HAKONE,\NUNDERGROUND TESTING FACILITY NO.2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.76,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}LCL pressure, +0.2.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:27.97,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}No destrudo readings in transmitter.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:31.72,default,,0,0,0,,-What is this child doing here?\N-That's Director Ikari's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:36.44,default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, this isn't a daycare center.\NToday is an important day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:40.06,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Sorry, Professor Fuyutsuki.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I was the one who brought him.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:43.40,default,,0,0,0,,Yui? This is {\i1\c&Hffffff&}your{\c}{\i0} experiment today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:47.53,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}That's exactly why. I want him to see{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}that he has a bright future ahead of him.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.78,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Those were Ms. Yui's last words.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:55.08,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}That freak accident wiped her{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}from the face of the earth.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.62,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Just as I had hoped.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.34,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'm a terrible woman, aren't I?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:05.88,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Ritchan, Director Ikari was{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}a changed man after that day.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.72,default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been all week?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:14.22,default,,0,0,0,,Grieve all you want, but remember that you\Nhave responsibilities beyond yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:19.73,default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware. Fuyutsuki,\NI'm proposing a new project today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.57,default,,0,0,0,,I've already submitted it\Nto Chairman Keel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:23.98,default,,0,0,0,,Surely you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:28.49,default,,0,0,0,,I do. The path to attain godhood,\Nwhich no one has ever achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.82,default,,0,0,0,,The Human Instrumentality Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:31.82,default,,0,0,0,,2008 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:36.04,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Mother, congratulations on completing{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}the basic theories for the Magi.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.62,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}To coincide with your success,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'm happy to tell you{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:41.63,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I've been informally accepted into Gehirn.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.92,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'm set to work as part of Project-E,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}starting next month.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.43,default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:57.02,default,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko Akagi, Technology\NDevelopment Department. My ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:01.35,default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the Command Center\Nhas been framed out, so I came to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.06,default,,0,0,0,,It's a real maze here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.86,default,,0,0,0,,The Director is there\Nwith Dr. Akagi right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.61,default,,0,0,0,,-Are you sure?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.16,default,,0,0,0,,I have no regrets about my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.95,default,,0,0,0,,Liar. You can't let go of Ms. Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.79,default,,0,0,0,,But I can live with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.13,default,,0,0,0,,2010 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.64,default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}GEO-FRONT ARTIFICIAL CANOPY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.60,default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}VENTRAL POINT DEFENSE EMPLACEMENT NO.2\N(PLANNED SITE)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.56,default,,0,0,0,,That's Gehirn HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.94,default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Director.\NYou have your son with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.65,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought you had a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:51.11,default,,0,0,0,,This isn't Shinji.\NI'm looking after a friend's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.11,default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.03,default,,0,0,0,,Hi there, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.83,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}She reminds me of someone...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.04,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Ms. Yui?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:05.75,default,,0,0,0,,All files pertaining to Rei Ayanami\Nhave been deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.75,default,,0,0,0,,She's a blank slate. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:11.01,default,,0,0,0,,SUPERCOMPUTER MAGI SYSTEM\NCOMPLETED
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:15.26,default,,0,0,0,,Magus Casper, Magus Balthasar,\Nand Magus Melchior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:20.06,default,,0,0,0,,The Magi are the three sides of me.\NMe as a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:23.64,default,,0,0,0,,Me as a mother. Me as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.27,default,,0,0,0,,Those three sides\Nare constantly vying for control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.11,default,,0,0,0,,Three of you, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.69,default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to power it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.45,default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving early today.\NMisato is coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:39.37,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.\NShe's also joined Gehirn, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:40.95,default,,0,0,0,,In Germany, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:43.25,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she works at the Third Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:46.71,default,,0,0,0,,-A long-distance relationship, then?\N-She says they broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.92,default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's too bad.\NThey seemed like the perfect couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.38,default,,0,0,0,,Men and women are hard to figure out.\NThere's no logic to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.72,default,,0,0,0,,Ever the aloof ice queen, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.64,default,,0,0,0,,Careful, happiness\Nis going to pass you by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.89,default,,0,0,0,,I have even more trouble with\Nhow to define happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:06.27,default,,0,0,0,,I should go. It's been forever\Nsince I went out for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.02,default,,0,0,0,,-Good work today.\N-You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.12,default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:25.96,default,,0,0,0,,I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.79,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Well, do you want me\Nto show you the way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.38,default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.76,default,,0,0,0,,But you can't find your way out\Nby yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.26,default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your help, you hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.55,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:42.10,default,,0,0,0,,I can find my own way out,\Nso leave me alone, you hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.98,default,,0,0,0,,Calling someone a hag is very rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.56,default,,0,0,0,,But you are one, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.52,default,,0,0,0,,You're making me angry.\NYou need a scolding from Director Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.40,default,,0,0,0,,-He's the one who says that about you.\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}-What?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:59.78,default,,0,0,0,,Things like, "That hag is such a nag."\NOr, "I don't need that hag anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:03.24,default,,0,0,0,,"That hag is such a nag."\N"I don't need that hag anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:09.25,default,,0,0,0,,"I don't need that hag anymore."\NHe's the one who says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.04,default,,0,0,0,,"I don't need that hag anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:22.26,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you die, there will be another\Nto take your place, Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.93,default,,0,0,0,,Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:37.44,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}On that day, the Human Instrumentality{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Project, chaired by Keel Lorenz,{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.32,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}dissolved Gehirn,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}its research organization.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.74,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The Special Agency Nerv was founded{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.95,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}as the execution organization{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}for all of its projects.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:49.04,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}And then we were all{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}transferred over to Nerv.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:50.54,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Except for Dr. Akagi,{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:54.38,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}the key figure behind{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}the development of the Magi System.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.55,default,,0,0,0,,2015 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.89,default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, it's you.\N-It's been a while, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:06.14,default,,0,0,0,,The guard outside is getting\Na little shut-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.48,default,,0,0,0,,Doing this will mean your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.98,default,,0,0,0,,I just want to get closer to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:13.52,default,,0,0,0,,The truth inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.49,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:23.87,default,,0,0,0,,-I'm free to go?\N-Yes. The issue has been resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:26.70,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.21,default,,0,0,0,,-And him?\N-Unknown, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.14,default,,0,0,0,,Hi. What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.44,default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.75,default,,0,0,0,,MESSAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.72,default,,0,0,0,,PLAY MESSAGES
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:35.81,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Hi, Katsuragi. It's me.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:41.28,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}By the time you get this message,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I've probably made life difficult for you.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:45.61,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Sorry about that.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}And apologize to Ritchan for me, okay?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:50.33,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I shouldn't be asking favors,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}but I've been growing some flowers.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:53.41,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}If you could water them for me,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'd appreciate it.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.00,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji knows where they are.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:02.34,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Katsuragi, the truth is with you.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Keep going and don't look back.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:07.01,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}If I see you again...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.14,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'll say the words that I couldn't{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}say to you eight years ago.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:11.89,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Bye.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.89,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Message left at 12:02 p.m.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.15,default,,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:23.61,default,,0,0,0,,You're such an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:50.26,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}All I could do was hide from Misato.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:55.35,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I knew there was nothing I could do.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Nothing I could say.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:58.35,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I was just a child.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.61,default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:11.22,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Asuka is in a mental downward spiral{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}over being one-upped by Shinji.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:13.68,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}And then a mental attack{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}unleashed by an Angel{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.76,0:23:15.64,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}delivers the final blow to her heart.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:18.81,default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji has no words{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}with which to console her.{\c}{\i0}
